727379f-a.title: Queens: Merrick Boulevard - Laurelton Parkway
727379f-a.text:
Merrick Boulevard, north side, between Laurelton Parkway and 234th Street, viewing west toward the latter and showing an old fnrmhouse. It was owned by A. Smith (Schmidt) in 1891
and 1909.
March 9, 1927
P. L. Sperr
